Package bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model

Class Booking

java.lang.Object
bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model.Booking
public class Booking extends Object
The Booking class represents a booking made by a customer for a flight in the Flight Booking System. It contains information such as the booking date, customer details, flight details, and booking status.
